      "widgets_values": [
        "ℹ️ S-15 LUT Import — apply a portable Adobe Cube 1.0 .cube file to any image\n\nChain: LoadImage → N-14 JHPixelProLUTImport (filename=\"pack_lut.cube\", strength=0.8) → PreviewImage.\n\nN-14 reads the .cube from ComfyUI's input/ directory (relative filename) or an absolute path, parses the 3D LUT into a tensor grid, and applies it via trilinear grid_sample. Works with any Adobe Cube 1.0 file — DaVinci Resolve exports, Premiere creative-look LUTs, Film Convert / IWLTBAP / Lutify.me / etc.\n\nROUND-TRIP DEMO: Run the S-14 workflow to export your ComfyUI color-grade chain as pack_lut.cube → copy the file from output/ to input/ → run this workflow to re-apply the grade on a fresh source image. The LUT is portable beyond ComfyUI.\n\nTUNABLES: strength in [0, 1] (0 = pass-through, 1 = full LUT, linear blend); optional MASK input gates the apply spatially (useful with S-05 Luminosity Masking or a face/skin segmentation mask).\n\nLIMITATIONS: trilinear interpolation (tetrahedral deferred v2); RGB-only (no alpha LUT); domain clamp (out-of-range colors held at boundary, no extrapolation)."
      ],
      "color": "#243",
      "bgcolor": "#365"
    }
